text: Strängnäs Cathedral () is a cathedral in the town of Strängnäs in Sweden. Belonging to Strängnäs Cathedral Parish with Aspö of the Church of Sweden, it serves the Diocese of Strängnäs, and has been supposed to been opened in on 29 June 1291. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden cathedrals Category:13th-century buildings and structures
title: Strängnäs Cathedral
